{
  "stem": "17606.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 252.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't realize this-- but this was the beginning, the corpses.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we organized also as civil disobedience group.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had patrol-- we were patrolling the streets and telling the Jews, don't go here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The-- the trucks are there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Don't go this way.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The trucks are there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Go-- safer to go this way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That was our main task till we went into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was November 15 of 1940.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's the-- the day when the ghetto--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--gates were closed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time, was one ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One ghetto.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then they started to cut and it became a small ghetto, a big ghetto, and a normal slant.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was in-- in the central ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With my parents.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Whatever you could carry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "NO.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A pushcart.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then it was--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--also a voluntary-- they-- because the decree for going to the ghetto was announced on-- just before Neilah on Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The whole day, we knew only some news was coming this afternoon.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's what I was aiming to tell you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a voluntary exchange of apartments.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The non-Jews who were living in the Jewish quarters could exchange apartments.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the demands for them, before they were-- before they were walking, living in an attic without the toilet, without any.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now they want a two-- two bathrooms and with this, and a three bedroom apartment or four bedroom apartment, in the most elaborate section of Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it-- some-- it was accommodated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There-- that's why it was postponed for two weeks, the moving.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "From the 1st of November to the 15th.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because it was such a nice exchange between the Poles and the Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Our apartment, a neighbor who was flirting with the-- with the-- with the Nazis, a woman, ripped our apartment-- our apartment.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
